    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve honestly babied this car since day one. There isn't a single scratch on it, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
